Achievements.Name: Lucky Charm
Achievements.Description: Hittin' that Golden Horseshoe was purdy hard, partner! Nicely done.

Achievements.Name: Cowboy Up
Achievements.Description: Congrats! You've unocked the County Fair. Good job.

Achievements.Name: 1st Pace
Achievements.Description: State Fair? Other than bacon, nothing is finer than earning an entry to a rodeo at the State Fair.

Achievements.Name: Top Notch
Achievements.Description: Lone Star. A single, stunning star, shimmering superbly. And now you can rodeo here.

Achievements.Name: Ain't too bad
Achievements.Description: Never forget to always remember to Remember The Alamo!

Achievements.Name: Reach for the Sky
Achievements.Description: If you go too far west, you'll end up wet. So just go Far West enough, and not any farther.

Achievements.Name: Now yer gettin' it
Achievements.Description: A longshot is a situation that defies the odds. Just like your rodeo skills! Keep it up.

Achievements.Name: Top Hand
Achievements.Description: Wow, you've done it! The ulitmate rodeo arena has been unlocked. You deserve it, and you're welcome!

Achievements.Name: Barrel Roll!
Achievements.Description: A barrel roll is a difficult act of skill and timing, and you just did one my friend!

Achievements.Name: Barrel of Monkeys
Achievements.Description: Nothing is more fun than a Barrel of Monkeys, except a whole lotta Barrel Racing!

Achievements.Name: A Fistful of Barrels
Achievements.Description: It would be hard to hold 100 barrels in a single fist, but I bet you would if you could.

Achievements.Name: A Few Barrels More
Achievements.Description: By a few, we meant 150 more than a fistful. But with your overachieving, we knew you'd be here soon.

Achievements.Name: Get a rope
Achievements.Description: How many wraps did you do? Most ropers only do two. This is not safe wrapping in my opinion.

Achievements.Name: Roped In
Achievements.Description: You got all gold in Tie Down Roping? Only the very best ropers can say that!

Achievements.Name: Piggin' it up
Achievements.Description: A Piggin String is used to hog tie a calf, not a pig. Weird.

Achievements.Name: High Noon
Achievements.Description: Shoot straight and move fast. Sounds easy, but it ain't.

Achievements.Name: Shoot 'Em Up
Achievements.Description: "Bang bang bang bang bang bang... click. Darn." -- an anonymous tombstone in Texas

Achievements.Name: Luftballons
Achievements.Description: You didn't let the red balloons go by.

Achievements.Name: What do I feel? Recoil.
Achievements.Description: No bullets are used in the real event, instead the blank ammo burns the balloons, popping them.

Achievements.Name: Team Up
Achievements.Description: There is no I in TEAM, but there is in WIN. You chose your partner well.

Achievements.Name: Cowboy and Woody
Achievements.Description: A lengendary roping team from Montgomery, TX. You aren't this good, but close.

Achievements.Name: Sheer Steer
Achievements.Description: You have roped over 48 metric tons of meat, here is your reward.

Achievements.Name: Sometimes you get the bull
Achievements.Description: And sometime he gets you. I mean a really deep understanding of your wants and needs.

Achievements.Name: No Bull
Achievements.Description: With an average skin thickness of over 1/4", a bull is only tickled by being spurred.

Achievements.Name: Rough Stock Rider
Achievements.Description: Well, that was a workout!

Achievements.Name: How now brown cow?
Achievements.Description: They keep gettin' in the way, dagnabbit!

Achievements.Name: Riding Herd
Achievements.Description: This says you are a quantity over quality kind of player. Still, nice work!

Achievements.Name: Gold Miner
Achievements.Description: While hard to rope, an El Dorado calf pays a handsome dividend, your portfolio thanks you.

Achievements.Name: Pistol Packin'
Achievements.Description: I'm thinkin' you like plinkin' by the way all those targets were sinkin'.

Achievements.Name: Rootin' Tootin' Shootin'
Achievements.Description: Now thats how you shoot!

Achievements.Name: Back in the Saddle again
Achievements.Description: Are we there yet? You certainly are. Huge kudos to you!

Achievements.Name: Till the Sun Goes Down
Achievements.Description: I bet the stars will be pretty tonight. Make a wish on one. I hope it comes true!

Achievements.Name: Till the Sun Comes Up
Achievements.Description: Go. To. Bed. Now.

Achievements.Name: Double the fun
Achievements.Description: Playing by yourself is no fun at all. The more, the merrier, right?

Achievements.Name: Three is a lovely number
Achievements.Description: A group dynamic consisting of three people can be stabilized with good humor and tact.

Achievements.Name: The Magnificent Four
Achievements.Description: Now THIS is a party!

Achievements.Name: Top Hand of the Rodeo
Achievements.Description: Thank you for playing!

Achievements.Name: Bunch of Hooey
Achievements.Description: A horse named "Booger"? Now that's just pure fun!

Achievements.Name: Bull in a China Shop
Achievements.Description: Admit it, you were tempted to knock the barrel over when you first saw it, right? Me too.

Achievements.Name: The One that got away
Achievements.Description: They do that sometimes. Only seems fair.

Achievements.Name: Time for Glasses
Achievements.Description: 20/10? More like 20/200! Either that, or you just crave achievements!

Achievements.Name: I thought YOU had him!
Achievements.Description: In any team, good communication is essential. By the way, you don't have it.

Achievements.Name: Humility is a virtue
Achievements.Description: Pride cometh with the fall. Afterall, you survived, didn't you?

Achievements.Name: Roped by a dope
Achievements.Description: Them calves ain't gonna catch themselves!

Achievements.Name: Cheap Shot
Achievements.Description: Even if you don't have any skills, ya gotta a lot of try in ya.

Achievements.Name: Gettin' all Hollywood
Achievements.Description: Everyone wants to be a cowboy.

Achievements.Name: BRB, feedin' mah horse
Achievements.Description: If you really did just feed your horse, I gotta admit, that's pretty awesome (and coincidental)!

Achievements.Name: Thanks!
Achievements.Description: That is a lot of people, huh?
